- I know it's a puppy.

116
00:09:36,285 --> 00:09:38,161
Put Tu-Tu on
and she'll go for a ride.

117
00:09:38,287 --> 00:09:40,622
- My Tu-Tu!
- I need one second.

118
00:09:40,706 --> 00:09:41,957
