used to call that squeaky stair?

207
00:15:27,761 --> 00:15:30,806
"The squeaky stair. "
[laughing]

208
00:15:30,931 --> 00:15:34,142
- [squeaking]
- [laughing]

209
00:15:42,526 --> 00:15:46,280
