I think it was...

215
00:16:01,044 --> 00:16:02,462
I think it was worth it.

216
00:16:02,546 --> 00:16:04,756
Man, this is great.
Man, this is the best.

217
00:16:04,882 --> 00:16:08,302
You guys sittin' around
