226
00:16:28,614 --> 00:16:29,865
Yeah, it is. Yeah.

227
00:16:29,990 --> 00:16:32,534
But you know, man,
I gotta tell ya,

228
00:16:32,618 --> 00:16:35,162
all these years I've been
avoiding Christmas,

229
00:16:35,245 --> 00:16:39,458
